      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is well-suited for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that may need a little extra care. The engine and transmission are fully functional, and the car handles predictably on the road. However, potential buyers should be aware of some cosmetic wear on the interior and minor exterior scuffs consistent with its age. While it runs well now, it will likely require some routine maintenance and minor part replacements in the near future to keep it in peak operating condition.",
