    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total beauty! This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm really sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make the next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43200.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
