    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and is protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather bolsters show zero wear or creasing, the carpets are pristine, and the original factory scent remains. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard, with a complete, documented service history from authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the undercarriage is spotless. All electronics, including the premium infotainment and driver-assist systems, operate exactly as they did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This sale includes both original master keys, the complete owner's manual portfolio, and a bespoke indoor car cover. This is a rare chance to acquire a flawless, investment-grade example of this model.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
